{
  "stem": "2581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were-- I think there were a lot of French people there in that camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, that camp became a Krankenlager, a camp especially for sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one would go out except it was called the latrine commander, which it's the, like, cess-- they would take out the cesspools to the-- to wherever they went.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what was the other one?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, and the dead-- the dead [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People that would take the dead people to bury them a few kilometers away from the-- from the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And most of the people had typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] What is it called?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Typhus that you get from lice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In German it's called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it's just typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typhus?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a different kind of typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typhoid, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Typhoid.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With all these languages I get a little confused.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Typhoid.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father had it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, before all this happened, I was picked to go with the dead-- with the-- to carry out the dead people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I fell down on my knees to the Lagerfuhrer, which was, itself, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was also a prisoner but people said he wasn't the worst of people, so I kneeled-- I bent down on my knees and I says, please, have mercy.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have never handled dead people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Give me any kind of work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For some reason, he picked-- he said, go to this bunker and work over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he sent me to chop on roots, you know, the roots from wood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Trees were brought to this place and I chopped it up and they kept themselves warm in there with these these kapos.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or they had this special, you know, these Lageralteste with his buddies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They lived in a special barrack, so they used that wood, what I chopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
